Package org.apache.turbine.services.mimetype.util

Class Summary
CharSetMap This class maintains a set of mappers defining mappings between locales and the corresponding charsets.
MimeType This class is used to represent parsed MIME types.
MimeTypeMap This class maintains a set of mappers defining mappings between MIME types and the corresponding file name extensions.
MimeTypeMapper This class defines mappings between MIME types and the corresponding file name extensions.
